<%= render 'shared/header', title: 'Think Green' %>
<section class="wrapper !bg-[#ffffff]">
  <div class="container pt-20 xl:pt-18 lg:pt-18 md:pt-18 pb-16 xl:pb-20 lg:pb-20 md:pb-20">
    <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-[-15px] xl:mx-[-35px] lg:mx-[-20px] mt-[-50px] items-center">
      <!-- Tekst sekcija -->
      <div class="w-full xl:w-12/12 lg:w-12/12 w-full flex-[0_0_auto] xl:px-[35px] lg:px-[20px] px-[15px] max-w-full mt-[50px] !relative">
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle1.svg", class: "h-9 !absolute xl:block lg:block", style: "top: -5%; left: -2%", alt: "doodle") %>
        <h2 class="text-[calc(1.305rem_+_0.66vw)] font-bold xl:text-[1.8rem] leading-[1.3] !mb-3">
A Business Cost We Can’t Ignore
        </h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We pay fees everywhere. Banks, transactions, online payments, card processing – everything comes at a price. We pay taxes on food, electricity, water, and everything else we consume. There’s a cost to every single thing we do.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">The only entity that doesn’t tax us is the planet itself. But we owe it everything.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">This is no longer about trends or corporate image – it’s about responsibility. Every business, no matter its size or industry, has a duty to rethink its impact and actively contribute to a more sustainable way of working.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">At MOO, we refuse to work with companies that actively pollute and damage the environment without a clear plan to reduce their carbon footprint. High carbon emissions with no accountability? That’s a hard no from us. Every business must be responsible for its impact, and those who refuse to acknowledge it won’t be part of our network.</p>
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle4.svg", class: "h-8 !absolute xl:block lg:block !rounded-[.4rem]", style: "bottom: -3%; right: 1%", alt: "doodle") %>
      </div>
      <!-- /.row -->
    </div>
    <!--/column -->
  </div>
  <!--/.row -->
</div>
<!-- /.container -->
</section>

