Putting Money Where It Matters
        </h2>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">Talk is cheap. Companies love to say they ‘care’ about sustainability, but the real question is – what are they actually doing?</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We’re making a commitment. A percentage of every transaction we process will be redirected to organisations focused on environmental protection. Whether it’s local initiatives, regional sustainability projects, or global efforts to tackle climate change, we want every deal we close to contribute to something bigger.</p>
        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">This isn’t about offsetting guilt. It’s about taking direct action and building a business model that considers the future, not just the bottom line.</p>
        <%= image_tag("svg/doodle4.svg", class: "h-8 !absolute xl:block lg:block !rounded-[.4rem]", style: "bottom: -3%; right: 1%", alt: "doodle") %>
