        <p class="lead !text-[1.05rem] !leading-[1.6] font-medium">We believe in carbon tracking as a standard business practice. Every company should know its impact and have a concrete plan to reduce it. We support projects and initiatives that enable businesses to monitor and cut emissions in a transparent, measurable way. Because accountability leads to progress.</p>
